<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:15:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着大型科技公司争先恐后地遵守欧盟规则，调查可能会发生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/big-tech-scrambles-meet-eu-rules-investigations-seen-likely-2024-03-07/</link><description>从彻底改革在线平台到幕后工程，谷歌、苹果、亚马逊、微软、Meta 和 TikTok 所有者字节跳动在过去六个月里都在努力遵守周四生效的具有里程碑意义的欧盟技术规则。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/big-tech-scrambles-meet-eu-rules-investigations-seen-likely-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>立陶宛称俄罗斯可以在乌克兰继续战斗至少两年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-can-fight-ukraine-least-two-years-lithuania-says-2024-03-07/</link><description>立陶宛情报机构周四在一份报告中表示，高油价、逃避制裁和国家投资正在为俄罗斯提供足够的资源，以目前的强度在乌克兰进行至少两年的战斗。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:34:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-can-fight-ukraine-least-two-years-lithuania-says-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港法官驳回亲民主电台主持人煽动叛乱案上诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</link><description>周四，三名香港高等法院法官驳回了著名民主活动人士谭德志的上诉，谭德志因 7 项煽动罪指控被定罪并被判 40 个月，他的律师辩称这些罪名是对言论自由的不成比例的限制。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>全球需求回升，中国出口超预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-trade-beats-forecasts-signals-global-trade-rebound-2024-03-07/</link><description>中国一月至二月的进出口增长超出预期，表明全球贸易正在出现拐点，这对试图支撑步履蹒跚的经济复苏的政策制定者来说是一个令人鼓舞的信号。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:34:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-trade-beats-forecasts-signals-global-trade-rebound-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国1-2月出口增长7.1%，进口增长3.5%，好于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-exports-rise-71-imports-grow-35-beating-forecasts-2024-03-07/</link><description>海关周四公布的数据显示，1-2月中国出口同比增长7.1%，进口增长3.5%，两项数据均好于预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:14:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-exports-rise-71-imports-grow-35-beating-forecasts-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业集团复星旗下旅游部门表示正在审查业务组合</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-conglomerate-fosuns-tourism-unit-says-reviewing-business-portfolio-2024-03-07/</link><description>复星旅文集团周四表示，正在审查其业务组合，以回应路透社有关其正在探索出售酒店度假村的报道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:09:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-conglomerate-fosuns-tourism-unit-says-reviewing-business-portfolio-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向六国旅客提供免签待遇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-offer-visa-free-travel-travellers-six-countries-2024-03-07/</link><description>外交部长王毅周四表示，中国将从3月14日起向瑞士、爱尔兰、匈牙利、奥地利、比利时和卢森堡公民提供免签旅行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-offer-visa-free-travel-travellers-six-countries-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市普遍走高；日本央行的讨论提振日元，打压日经指数</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-07/</link><description>周四，亚洲股市大多上涨，原因是越来越多的迹象表明美联储将很快开始降息，投资者对此感到安慰，而有关日本即将实施政策转变的传言提振了日元，并将日经指数从历史高位拉低。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:35:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>外长称美国对中国有错误认知</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-has-wrong-perception-china-says-foreign-minister-2024-03-07/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周四表示，尽管自去年 11 月拜登总统和习近平主席会晤以来取得了一些进展，但美国仍坚持对中国的错误认知，尚未兑现其“承诺”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-has-wrong-perception-china-says-foreign-minister-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中俄加强新型合作、巩固友谊</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-foster-new-cooperation-consolidate-friendship-with-russia-2024-03-07/</link><description>外交部长王毅在北京举行的年度议会会议期间举行的新闻发布会上表示，中方愿与俄方一道，培育合作新动能，巩固友谊。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-foster-new-cooperation-consolidate-friendship-with-russia-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>乐观的中国贸易数据推动油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-edge-higher-after-us-stocks-build-less-than-expected-2024-03-07/</link><description>周四油价保持稳定，在乐观的中国贸易数据以及美国数据显示原油库存增幅小于预期以及燃料库存大幅减少后，维持隔夜涨幅。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:50:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-edge-higher-after-us-stocks-build-less-than-expected-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>防务报告称，中国加强灰色地带战以消耗台湾资源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-grey-zone-warfare-exhaust-taiwan-defence-report-says-2024-03-07/</link><description>台湾国防部周四的一份报告称，中国加强了针对台湾的灰色地带战，旨在让这个民主岛屿周围的地区充满气球、无人机和民用船只。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-steps-up-grey-zone-warfare-exhaust-taiwan-defence-report-says-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>日元因日本央行即将转向支点的可能性而上涨；美元普遍走低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-falls-with-treasury-yields-views-looming-us-rate-cuts-2024-03-07/</link><description>日元兑美元汇率周四升至一个月高位，因越来越多的人猜测日本央行(BOJ)可能最早在本月结束负利率，以及美国即将降息的押注拖累美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:21:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-falls-with-treasury-yields-views-looming-us-rate-cuts-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>经济不景气，更多中国女性选择单身</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-chinese-women-choosing-singledom-economy-stutters-2024-03-07/</link><description>自由撰稿人柴婉柔认为婚姻是一种不公平的制度。和中国许多年轻女性一样，她是一场不断发展的运动的一部分，该运动设想了一个没有丈夫和孩子的未来，这给政府带来了一个本来可以不做的挑战。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:10:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/more-chinese-women-choosing-singledom-economy-stutters-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚和越南升级关系，开始就关键矿产进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-upgrades-relations-with-vietnam-strategic-partnership-2024-03-07/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·艾博内塞周四表示，该国正在将与越南的关系提升至全面战略伙伴关系的水平，并就矿产进行年度对话，以推动供应链多元化，远离中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:06:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-upgrades-relations-with-vietnam-strategic-partnership-2024-03-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>